article_id:1005,category_name:News,title_name:Daily Free Summon Event Incoming!,image_path:,message:<div>A daily free summon event, which will allow you to summon on the applicable summon showcases for free once per day, starts <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1578981600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1578981600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1579759140"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcases</div><div>You can summon on each of the following summon showcases for free once per day.</div><div><br></div><div>・Windswept Harbingers</div><div><br></div><div>Note: You can perform up to nine summons during the nine-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1578981600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1579759140"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Flames of Reflection</div><div><br></div><div>Note: You can perform up to nine summons during the nine-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1578981600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1579759140"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 6:00 AM to 5:59 AM the next day).</div><div>2. The daily free summon resets each day at 6:00 AM.</div><div>3. The Daily Deal, which allows you to summon once per day for 30 diamantium, can be used after performing your daily free summon.</div><div>4. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1578895200,update_time1578552952